But let’s dwell on that word a moment.  Who is being wronged by the theoretical classification of a movie?  Is there some grand union of fantasy writers stomping about in their libraries up in arms over this slight?  Is JRR Tolkien rolling in his grave?  Ya think maybe living in outrage culture has gotten to you?  Just because a headline wants you to be outraged for clicks…doesn’t mean that you actually have to be outraged.  You could be better than that.

